window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Untouchables. That's what everyone calls them. At least, it's my best friend's nickname for them. And since she's the only one that talks to me at my new school, I'll take her word for it.</p> <p>The nickname probably comes from the fact that they're exorbitantly wealthy. Old wealth. The kind that isn't flaunted around. But you can tell by the way they carry themselves. Or maybe the name just refers to the fact that they're so beautiful it's almost hard to look at them.</p> <p>No matter the reason for their nickname, it's an ironic one. I've only been going to this school for a week, and I already want to touch.</p>"; 
